Spain Chooses RBS For Sale of Aena Airport Operator

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-06-20T18:26:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/spain-chooses-rbs-for-sale-of-aena-airport-operator.html
Spain  chose  Royal Bank of Scotland
Group Plc (RBS)  to coordinate the sale of as much as 49 percent of
airport operator Aena Aeropuertos, the state-run company said in
a statement on its website today. The bank will also coordinate
tenders for management contracts, Aena said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  